00:18:40.540 --> 00:18:43.980
sequences. And what we did here was try to use

308
00:18:44.020 --> 00:18:47.840
computational prediction tools to predict the function of that sequence.

309
00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:51.090
We predicted where CpG islands would be in genes.

