314
00:19:06.320 --> 00:19:08.620
support in Pfam, et cetera.

315
00:19:09.500 --> 00:19:13.020
So these sequences represent non-repetitive sequence

316
00:19:13.080 --> 00:19:16.660
with coding and regulatory

317
00:19:16.700 --> 00:19:20.520
features that exist outside of the current reference framework.

318
00:19:20.960 --> 00:19:24.420
So you can see here we see widespread expression, not only in

