337
00:20:30.400 --> 00:20:33.440
not mean it's representative of your given population.

338
00:20:33.940 --> 00:20:37.120
And this has staggering consequences for precision oncology,

339
00:20:37.640 --> 00:20:40.060
including affecting somatic variant calling,

340
00:20:41.140 --> 00:20:44.809
neoantigen or HLA typing, et cetera, as well as our ability

