342
00:20:48.380 --> 00:20:51.480
And so I will end with these set of practical

343
00:20:51.540 --> 00:20:55.180
recommendations that we need to have a more measured

344
00:20:55.260 --> 00:20:56.420
approach to

345
00:20:57.380 --> 00:21:00.880
