351
00:21:20.020 --> 00:21:22.180
And so we should shift to think about

352
00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:24.240
sequence completeness

353
00:21:25.960 --> 00:21:29.320
relative to population representativeness.

354
00:21:29.980 --> 00:21:33.680
I went through a very complex set of analyses.

